      <title>Gol 计划筹集 15 亿美元新股以偿还融资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/gol-looks-to-raise-1-5-billion-in-new-equity-to-repay-financing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据新的五年财务计划，巴西航空公司 Gol Linhas Aereas Inteligentes SA 计划筹集 15 亿美元的新股本，以偿还现有的债务人持有融资并支撑其资产负债表。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/gol-looks-to-raise-1-5-billion-in-new-equity-to-repay-financing</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 15:43:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对加拿大降息的押注为落后银行带来希望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/bets-on-canada-rate-cut-hold-out-hope-for-underperforming-banks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[多伦多湾街上下的投资者越来越多地押注加拿大六月降息，这可能会提振加拿大长期低迷的银行股。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/bets-on-canada-rate-cut-hold-out-hope-for-underperforming-banks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 14:57:04 GMT</pubDate>
